Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: vectors

Control measures
Measures applied: movement control inside the country; screening; zoning; vaccination permitted (if a vaccine exists); no treatment of affected animals
Measures to be applied: no other measures

Diagnostic test results
Laboratory name and type:
Experimental Zooprophylactic Institute (IZSAM), Teramo (national laboratory)
Species / Test / Test date / Result
Sheep / polymerase chain reaction (PCR) / 1 Sep 2016 / Positive
Sheep / polymerase chain reaction (PCR)/ 7 Sep 2016 / Positive

Future reporting
The event is continuing. Weekly follow-up reports will be submitted.

